{
  "stem": "18670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would sit in the no man's land 'til after dark just to turn around and come back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And today you read Mexicans are doing a very similar thing, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had no intentions of going back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No matter what they do I was going to stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened after you settled in?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you remain in that with these people?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not too long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- what actually happened is between Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur-- when I crossed the border, I must have hurt myself somewhere.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a scratch on my left arm and I got blood poisoning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even my glands under my left arm were swollen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And normally you would have gone to the Jewish committee to see a Jewish doctor there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They take care of you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But again, we're in this period of Munich and the committee was closed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Belgium was actually preparing for war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's what it looked like.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wound up in the Catholic hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from Yom Kippur, I spent the night in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They cleaned it up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put me on I don't know what medication.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think they had antibiotics in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, I got out of the hospital on Yom Kippur and had another experience.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, walking out, I always observed Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always fasted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't have any food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I walked by the temple and I heard the prayers and I walked inside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was usher standing there, right up there near the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I asked them whether I could sit down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I told them I just came out of the hospital and I escaped from Austria and Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, get-- go upstairs and get a ticket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
